Description: Thank you for visiting our ebay store! Vera Bradley's durable and very large Vera Trimmed Traveler tote is made of soft quilted fabric with a removable sturdy fabric covered bottom insert. The recessed zippered top closure secures an interior featuring 6 roomy open slip pockets. There is also an open slip pocket on the exterior front. The chic faux leather dual straps have a comfortable drop of about 11 inches, and are sewn from the bottom, all the way up each side. The Trimmed Traveler is versatile - use it for travel, as an overnight bag, a baby bag, or for gym, dance or gymnastics for yourself or for children. It is lightweight, and easily maintained with spot cleaning.
